                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.00111 Lic. <hi rend="superscript">Vimalert Co.
                        Ltd./52</hi>/25: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in Spam</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bowers</hi>
                    </persName>), <hi rend="italic">Then in France</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-12-31T17:00:00-05:00"
                            >December 31, 1936—5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>B–101. Your 190, December 31, 11 a.m. The word “faction” has not been used in any
                    official statement of this Government with regard to the exportation of
                    munitions of war to Spain. The point which you make will be kept in mind and
                    brought to the attention of the proper persons when an opportunity offers.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Moore</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
